Subject: plymouthd.defaults: Enable UseSimpledrm=1

Show the splash screen as soon as possible.

Bug: https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/plymouth/plymouth/-/issues/110
Bug-Ubuntu: https://launchpad.net/bugs/1869655
Forwarded: not-needed
---
 src/plymouthd.defaults | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/plymouthd.defaults b/src/plymouthd.defaults
index 1a6327f..7b80691 100644
--- a/src/plymouthd.defaults
+++ b/src/plymouthd.defaults
@@ -3,3 +3,4 @@
 [Daemon]
 ShowDelay=0
 DeviceTimeout=8
+UseSimpledrm=1
